Federal Antitrust Service of the country in accordance with the Decree of the Government of the Russian Federation No. 2 "On the introduction of changes in the Regulations of the wholesale market of electricity and power and in the consolidated forecast balance of production and supply of electrical energy (power) within the framework of the Unified Energy System of Russia" (Business of the Russian Federation) 17.07
