The National Union of Unskilled, Municipal and Boiler Workers (GMB) is concerned about the investment at McVitie's factory in Glasgow
The union demands guarantees from the managers of the biscuit manufacturer McVitie's in connection with its long-term commitment to produce at the Glasgow plant.
